SELECT make_date(year, month_number, 1),  
    CASE 
      WHEN '${graph_type}' = 'oee' AND SUM(pbt) <> 0 AND SUM(apt) <> 0 AND SUM(gq+sq) <> 0 THEN ( (SUM(apt) / SUM(pbt)) * (SUM(pru * (gq+sq)) / SUM(apt)) * (SUM(gq) / SUM(gq+sq)) )
      WHEN '${graph_type}' = 'availability' AND SUM(pbt) <> 0 THEN SUM(apt) / SUM(pbt)
      WHEN '${graph_type}' = 'performance' AND SUM(apt) <> 0 THEN SUM(pru * (gq+sq)) / SUM(apt)
      WHEN '${graph_type}' = 'quality' AND SUM(gq+sq) <> 0 THEN SUM(gq) / SUM(gq+sq)
      ELSE NULL  
    END AS metric_value
FROM data_value 
INNER JOIN time ON data_value.time_id = time.time_id
WHERE equipment_id IN (1,2,3)
GROUP BY month_number, year
ORDER BY month_number

targets.rawSql:
SELECT CASE WHEN SUM(pbt) <> 0 THEN SUM(apt) / SUM(pbt) ELSE NULL END AS AVAILABILITY
FROM data_value INNER JOIN time ON data_value.time_id = time.time_id
WHERE equipment_id IN (1,2,3) AND data_value.time_id BETWEEN to_char(to_timestamp($__from / 1000), 'YYYYMMDD')::INTEGER AND to_char(to_timestamp($__to / 1000), 'YYYYMMDD')::INTEGER

SELECT CASE WHEN SUM(apt) <> 0 THEN SUM(pru * (gq+sq)) / SUM(apt) ELSE NULL END AS EFFECTIVENESS
FROM data_value INNER JOIN time ON data_value.time_id = time.time_id
WHERE equipment_id IN (1,2,3) AND data_value.time_id BETWEEN to_char(to_timestamp($__from / 1000), 'YYYYMMDD')::INTEGER AND to_char(to_timestamp($__to / 1000), 'YYYYMMDD')::INTEGER

SELECT CASE WHEN SUM(gq+sq) <> 0 THEN SUM(gq) / SUM(gq+sq) ELSE NULL END AS QUALITY_RATIO
FROM data_value INNER JOIN time ON data_value.time_id = time.time_id
WHERE equipment_id IN (1,2,3) AND data_value.time_id BETWEEN to_char(to_timestamp($__from / 1000), 'YYYYMMDD')::INTEGER AND to_char(to_timestamp($__to / 1000), 'YYYYMMDD')::INTEGER

SELECT
		ph.part_number_id AS CODE,
		CONCAT(LPAD(FLOOR(AVG(dv.apt) / 3600)::VARCHAR,'2','0'), ':', LPAD(FLOOR((AVG(dv.apt) % 3600) / 60)::VARCHAR, '2', '0')) AS AVG_PROD_TIME,
		((sum(dv.gq) + sum(dv.sq))::INTEGER)::VARCHAR AS TOTAL,
		(sum(dv.gq)::INTEGER)::VARCHAR AS GOOD,
		(sum(dv.sq)::INTEGER)::VARCHAR AS SCRAP,
		CASE WHEN (sum(dv.gq) + sum(dv.sq) <> 0) THEN CONCAT ((((sum(dv.gq) / (sum(dv.gq) + sum(dv.sq)) * 100)::INTEGER)::VARCHAR) , '') ELSE NULL END AS GOOD_PERC
FROM phase AS ph INNER JOIN data_value AS dv ON ph.phase_id = dv.phase_id
WHERE dv.time_id BETWEEN to_char(to_timestamp($__from / 1000), 'YYYYMMDD')::INTEGER AND to_char(to_timestamp($__to / 1000), 'YYYYMMDD')::INTEGER
GROUP BY ph.part_number_id
ORDER BY ph.part_number_id ASC
